::Prowl::

Prowl looks into Iron Raptor's optics as she looks at him, love surfacing 
above the concern in his. He shruggs as he hears her question.

"Sitting here for now," he says, leaning forward and looking into her optics, 
the concern once again showing in his optics, "Are you allright?"
